defaultStudents leave the Arava Institute poised to cooperatively implement initiatives that raise public awareness about forgiveness, peace, and sustainability. These young leaders are building a more peaceful and sustainable future
default in the Middle East, the United States, and throughout the world.  The Arava Alumni Peace and Environmental Network (AAPEN) supports
default over 800
default alumni in maintaining connections with each other and serves as a forum for the exchange of ideas and creation of new initiatives, functioning as a network of young professionals working on peace and the environment in the Middle East.
default&#xa0;
